<div class="panel">
  <div class="panel-heading">CreativeElements – How to use</div>
  <p>Insert a <strong>Hook</strong> widget in CE and enter a hook name, e.g. <code>displayWiseBlockUnderCart</code>
     or any custom hook created in this module (e.g. <code>displayWiseBlockUnderPrice</code>).</p>
  <p>Then create a content block in the module and assign it to this hook along with targeting rules (categories/tags).</p>
</div>
